Cyber Claw:



Cyber Claw tensed as Dinobot approached her, applying all threat. She bared 
her teeth back, sunk down, tail twitching violently. Her chest rose and sank 
rapidly. Her breathing was rapid. The closer he got, the tenser she got.

After he spoke to her, she erupted. He lunged out at him, with her sickle 
claws on her inner toes out. He flew past him, scraping him across the 
chest, and landed a few feet by the door.

She screeched and flashed her claws. She bit at the air.

"Stay away from me!" she screamed, her voice a little high in panic. "Stay 
away from me you stupid Maximals!"
